
ticks off 'Replaces previous security deposit no ' in the Official Receipt box of the Security Deposit
form, and add the previous deposit number;


for the CBSA, forward copy 2 of the BSF579 to CBSA Revenue Accounting and Reporting Division,
355 North River Road, 18th Floor, Ottawa, ON K1A 0L8; and


for IRCC, forward copy 2 of the BSF579 to Accounting Operations, Revenue Unit, NHQ, 70
Crémazie Street, Gatineau, QC, K1A 1L1 .

Procedures to reduce the amount of the original deposit

To reduce the amount of the original deposit, the CBSA or IRCC officer:


completes a Requisition for Refund / Forfeiture of Security Deposit form [IMM 0709B] to request a
partial refund of the original deposit;

